    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly a little sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-parked and pampered with regular detailing. You won't find a single blemish or scratch anywhere! It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come take a look, I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love at first sight!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2011 BMW M3 Coupe featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This specimen remains in impeccable mechanical health, boasting a precision-tuned double-VANOS system and individual throttle bodies that deliver a razor-sharp 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis maintains its factory rigidity, complemented by a slick-shifting Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and Electronic Damper Control (EDC). Every body panel retains its original factory finish, and the undercarriage is free of oxidation. Recent preventative maintenance includes documented rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring this high-performance machine is turn-key for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. No accidents. Clean title. Garage kept. Full service history included.",
      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality masterpiece that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, and it shows. The exterior paint retains a mirror-like depth with a professional ceramic coating, showing zero stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the factory alloy wheels are entirely free of curb rash, wrapped in brand-new Michelin Pilot Sport tires. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats remain firm and supple with no bolster wear or fading, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. All electronic systems, from the premium surround-sound audio to the adaptive navigation, function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by master technicians. We have a complete binder of service records, two sets of keys, and the original window sticker. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade vehicle for someone who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical secondary market offering. This vehicle remains in showroom-state, characterized by an unblemished exterior and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Every aspect of this motorcar has been curated for the individual who demands nothing short of perfection. An acquisition of this caliber represents a rare opportunity to secure a vehicle of unrivaled preservation and mechanical excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
