    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This absolute beauty is in mint condition and has been totally babied since day one. It drives like a dream, looks stunning, and I\u2019ve kept it sparkling inside and out. You\u2019ve gotta see this one in person\u2014it's a total gem and ready for its next home!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
