      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 that defines mechanical perfection. This example features the S54 3.2L power plant, characterized by its high-revving nature and individual throttle bodies. The high-pressure VANOS system has been fully overhauled with upgraded seals, and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement, paired with a limited-slip differential and a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. Suspension dynamics are enhanced by a Bilstein coilover suite, ensuring optimal roll center and damping. The exterior retains its factory luster with zero oxidation, while the cabin remains a time capsule of Nappa leather and intact trim. A turn-key masterpiece for the serious enthusiast.",
